➜走进上汽大众长沙工厂，探秘斯柯达完美品质——车媒“老鸟”圆梦之旅
http://www.sohu.com/a/428389964_99994080	29465
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201030/c1fb8a86033d47f0bc535aef1348c96b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201030/15b5b9f0d4c04c2cad9dff357976386b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
