➜新势力勐兽新消息，高合HiPhi X试生产下线，预计明年上半年交付
http://www.sohu.com/a/428426595_99994080	39033
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201030/ae48db952fd5429e8d11920a1fc20877.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201030/7747eef01b674a8283eb36cc80e5e767.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201030/5682f4ae5ff34a6b9951347fd82723a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
